snippet.title: Innocent Life Special Edition - Opening
snippet.description:
The OP to ILSE! Short, but pretty cool. I love the music in this game... so atmospheric sometimes.

I just got this game yesterday (Amazon took forever to ship it!! Well, it was super saver shipping after all o_o) and I'm loving it so far~

 It's the newest release in the Harvest Moon series, a port of the PSP game. I don't have a PSP so this is the first time I get to try it :)

It's getting a bit tedious, though. So I'm juggling playing this, BokuMono3, and Another Wonderful Life to keep myself from tiring out.
